      "title": "The 22nd Amendment to the Constitution was published in the Gazette",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The 22nd Amendment to the Constitution was submitted to the last Cabinet by Justice Minister Wijetasa Rajapaksa.",
        "In this context, it is noteworthy that the Gazette Notification regarding the draft Amendment Bill has been published in the Gazette at the same time as the approval was given at the last Cabinet meeting to submit it to Parliament."
